### 12.1 [HAPPY] List customers
GET {{base}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenK}}
{{accept}}

### 12.2 [HAPPY] Create customer manually
# @name createCustomer
POST {{base}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenK}}
{{contentJson}}
{{accept}}

{
  "name": "Test Customer Ltd",
  "email": "test@customer.com",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "gstin": "27AABCU9603R1ZX",
  "address": "123 Test Street, Mumbai",
  "marketplace": "amazon"
}

###
@customerId = {{createCustomer.response.body.data.id}}

### 12.3 [HAPPY] Get customer purchases
GET {{base}}/customers/{{customerId}}/purchases
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenK}}
{{accept}}

### 12.4 [SAD] Get another user's customer → 404
GET {{base}}/customers/{{customerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenR}}
{{accept}}


